# Data Availability for [Cation Disorder in AgSbTe2 Leads to Glasslike Ultralow Lattice Thermal Conductivity]

* `L1_1`: contains processed data files for L1_1 phase
* `D4`: contains processed data files for D4 phase
* `R1`: contains processed data files for R1 phase

---

In each folder,


## 1. Thermal Transport Results (BTE outputs)

Files prefixed with `BTE.*` contain phonon thermal transport properties calculated using ShengBTE.

Detailed descriptions of each output format and calculation procedure follow the standard ShengBTE workflow (see ShengBTE documentation).


---

## 2. Interatomic Force Constants

* `*.conf`: input configuration files for Phononpy
* `FORCE_CONSTANTS_2ND`, `FORCE_CONSTANTS_3RD`: second- and third-order interatomic force constants
* `POSCAR`: crystal structure input
* `band.dat`: phonon dispersion data
* `projected_dos.dat`: phonon partial density of states data

---

## 3. Post-processing and Plotting Scripts

* `3dplot-cube.py`: 3D visualization of OD-K
* `bs_pdos_onceplt.py`: band structure and phonon DOS plotting
* `offdgnl.out`: OD-K result calculated using Unified Kappa 


